  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fear often originates from deep within ourselves, and we are merely the ones who awaken it.</strong></h2><br><strong>\"18 Hell:Lost\" is a psychological horror indie game.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story:</strong></h2>Set in the bustling Shanghai of the Republic of China era, you awaken from a deep slumber on a couch, feeling disoriented and restless. Only then do you realize that you are trapped in a grand Shanghai hotel, unable to escape. Fate and soul intertwine, creating a complex tapestry... As you slowly explore the mysteries within, you find yourself sinking deeper into the unknown...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/ef97cdbb7febd9fae38e996c880ec996.poster.avif?t=1740426468\" width=526 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/ef97cdbb7febd9fae38e996c880ec996.webm?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/ef97cdbb7febd9fae38e996c880ec996.mp4?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Genre:</strong></h2>This game focuses on psychological horror, rather than direct displays of violence or monsters. It invokes fear in players through environmental design, music, storytelling, and other non-visual means.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/b03853976690a961c58ff512ed947f45.poster.avif?t=1740426468\" width=526 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/b03853976690a961c58ff512ed947f45.webm?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/b03853976690a961c58ff512ed947f45.mp4?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></h2>Through fragmented storytelling, players unlock the backstory and gain knowledge of Chinese folklore while experiencing a captivating suspenseful narrative. The game employs a \"maze\" mechanism, where players repeatedly find themselves trapped in a looping space, with time overlapping, guiding them to unearth the truth behind the events.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/d1cc281333602dcc81099001b818b946.poster.avif?t=1740426468\" width=388 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/d1cc281333602dcc81099001b818b946.webm?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/d1cc281333602dcc81099001b818b946.mp4?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fear often originates from deep within ourselves, and we are merely the ones who awaken it.</strong></h2><br><strong>\"18 Hell:Lost\" is a psychological horror indie game.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story:</strong></h2>Set in the bustling Shanghai of the Republic of China era, you awaken from a deep slumber on a couch, feeling disoriented and restless. Only then do you realize that you are trapped in a grand Shanghai hotel, unable to escape. Fate and soul intertwine, creating a complex tapestry... As you slowly explore the mysteries within, you find yourself sinking deeper into the unknown...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/ef97cdbb7febd9fae38e996c880ec996.poster.avif?t=1740426468\" width=526 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/ef97cdbb7febd9fae38e996c880ec996.webm?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/ef97cdbb7febd9fae38e996c880ec996.mp4?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Genre:</strong></h2>This game focuses on psychological horror, rather than direct displays of violence or monsters. It invokes fear in players through environmental design, music, storytelling, and other non-visual means.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/b03853976690a961c58ff512ed947f45.poster.avif?t=1740426468\" width=526 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/b03853976690a961c58ff512ed947f45.webm?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/b03853976690a961c58ff512ed947f45.mp4?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></h2>Through fragmented storytelling, players unlock the backstory and gain knowledge of Chinese folklore while experiencing a captivating suspenseful narrative. The game employs a \"maze\" mechanism, where players repeatedly find themselves trapped in a looping space, with time overlapping, guiding them to unearth the truth behind the events.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/d1cc281333602dcc81099001b818b946.poster.avif?t=1740426468\" width=388 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/d1cc281333602dcc81099001b818b946.webm?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773230/extras/d1cc281333602dcc81099001b818b946.mp4?t=1740426468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
